{"tid":1461647,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我媽媽經歷過文化大革命，有少少野想同大家講［2］","createTime":"2019-08-13T08:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T10:19:49.000Z","uid":63822,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7c6a364d03e827c5a31fc0eb4673141588f1cba0","tid":1461647,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:46:03.000Z","msg":"現時我地有幾樣野一定要改，如果唔係呢場仗就冇得打<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 社運生態</span><br />\n<br />\n社運 vs 競選<br />\n<br />\n我覺得香港人將競選同社運混淆左。<br />\n<br />\n競選先需要無限地爭取民意，愈多票愈好，要既民意永遠唔會話「夠啦」。<br />\n<br />\n而社運只要有足夠數量既人，可以負擔到足以推翻政府既行動，就已經足夠。<br />\n<br />\n話需如此，更多既民意當然可以錦上添花，但絕不要被民意自我綑綁。<br />\n<br />\n呢個問題大家要認真思考。正因為長毛、毓民等一班用社運黎助選既人，玩左咁多年，令好多香港人潛而默化，用競選既心態去搞社運。<br />\n<br />\n搞清楚兩者既出發點會令你睇清楚好多野。<br />\n<br />\n好坦白講，我地並唔需要太多民意，只要人手足夠做到要做既目標就可以。<br />\n<br />\n唔同競選，唔需要無限民意。<br />\n<br />\n打個比喻，假設有100個人做出抗爭就已經可推翻極權既時候，係唔係真係要為左唔影響50個中立派而放棄抗爭，由得極權繼續張牙舞爪？<br />\n<br />\n當然，我認為目前既民意要完全推翻政府仲係未夠。不過應付現階段抗爭已經足夠，目前應以抗爭活動成效為主，民意為副地決定抗爭如何進行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 文宣</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y82jqf3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY82jqf3.jpg&h=f6409a76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對家既文宣，係十分work既<br />\n<br />\n我地唔係新聞報導，係做文宣<br />\n<br />\n我地既責任唔係報導真相，係炒作同抹黑<br />\n<br />\n分唔清就永遠唔洗贏文宣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZYOq5gG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZYOq5gG.jpg&h=c6465310&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n都係對家既文宣<br />\n<br />\n文宣唔係百科全書，唔係要講道理，係要煽情<br />\n<br />\n睇得文宣圖好多都係唔想思考，冇心機分析你既大道理<br />\n<br />\n用震撼既畫面煽情，帶動情緒，甚至仇恨，呢個係共產黨成功之道<br />\n<br />\n何況鬧抹黑我地係有優勢，因為80%既藍絲都唔會做fact check。<br />\n<br />\n想要民意就唔該屈得就屈，要抹黑而唔係唱衰，否則輿論戰係唔會贏。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 勇武</span><br />\n<br />\n而家明就一定唔夠打，所以要打游擊戰，黑暗果隻<br />\n<br />\n禍一定要及妻兒<br />\n<br />\n取易不取難係游擊既甚本<br />\n<br />\n所以一定要麻包袋，而且仲要麻包袋佢全家<br />\n<br />\n對面玩白色恐怖，我地都要黑色恐怖<br />\n<br />\n邊個縮先就邊個輸，任人施壓，唔威嚇返對面就等輸。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n最後，有一樣算係off topic既野要講一講既。<br />\n<br />\n我地其實有好多野做出黎，係唔會失民心，只係我地諗得太多，例如一連三日和你飛，之前有好多擔憂，有人甚至想取消。萬幸係最後如期進行，民心有增無減。<br />\n<br />\n反而，好多地方我地唔應失民心既地方，偏偏失哂民心，以下一點我認為必須立即，係立即改變既地方：<br />\n<br />\n唔好屌人影相<br />\n<br />\n公眾場合係任何人都可以影相拍片既，人地並冇錯。<br />\n<br />\n我地唔想見光就要包實d自己，責任在我地，而唔係拍攝者。<br />\n<br />\n而且你屌人影相係 一。D。用。都。冇<br />\n<br />\n每一次出黎，最低消費都會佔返三五七條路。你認為當你係馬路上行走，而呢個時代架架車都有cam，路人唔影相鏡頭就捕捉唔到你咩？<br />\n<br />\n屌人影相不但保護唔到自己，仲會令市民反感。而呢d民意可能本來係屬於我地既，就咁樣白白比我地屌走左。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命。</span></span>"},{"pid":"670cc12e83d8886e633319bc90def1287bd1a7e8","tid":1461647,"uid":262389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:46:15.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"e0a0359addff078d2f82c05ccec766b63a9810bc","tid":1461647,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:49:55.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"b159c12c49d17f6ccd6e45dc0a3f4345d662217f","tid":1461647,"uid":292536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:50:55.000Z","msg":"推，革命就係宣傳，民意永遠都唔需要理會，革命成功之後就乜都得。點解原先講話要核爆度唔割席，就係呢個道理。而家欠缺嘅就係好好嘅文宣（propaganda）你無就打定輸數算。"},{"pid":"5b029da57b764a0fd73793b958e2aa4287934a6f","tid":1461647,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0a0359addff078d2f82c05ccec766b63a9810bc","tid":1461647,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:49:55.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:53:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e3528d7ab936fd917b77540b3c8c0b218d855ebd","tid":1461647,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:02:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af94f7281a99cd97be22fe2dd1c99142eefc9db1","tid":1461647,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:03:55.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"68ce0e4550aaebc333f5f8f1e42eec8d98d29266","tid":1461647,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:04:05.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"d57b7e8b19144bb662eb3ef9a8edc770f8accba9","tid":1461647,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:04:18.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"a01cf30ac38d6fc25461f4a82a10e6f313c5e04b","tid":1461647,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:04:32.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"6cc636e5f5eb94a17507188b783aa2ae59c57242","tid":1461647,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:04:49.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"0035a9587866abc6709a2fec530517c0d6a1e5c2","tid":1461647,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:05:02.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"d7df3f4368d4a938f0183f757c9facb01d575d8d","tid":1461647,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:05:17.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"e15aee8c6187dd9a3014e8825f018a2be339a476","tid":1461647,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:05:32.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"a8f38fb152391808eb24af27f44c53e8b814c5b5","tid":1461647,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:05:51.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"f6a2d4c44027adb1f41a5a2f3e2450031946cc55","tid":1461647,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:06:35.000Z","msg":"background information re-post:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大陸<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">細路 6-14 歲</span></span> --&gt; <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「中國少年先鋒隊」</span></span>（中國少先隊／少先隊）<br />\n「中國少先隊申請人的加入年齡必須介於6歲至14歲間[4]，<span style=\"color: teal;\">幾乎所有小學生都加入了少先隊。截至2002年，少先隊員1.3億人，成為世界上規模最大的先鋒組織</span>。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/中國少年先鋒隊\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%88%E9%8B%92%E9%9A%8A&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDby6Ol0HYJA13lVA%2BPgi6hPY%3D&h=7407306b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/中國少年先鋒隊</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大陸<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">青少年 14-28 歲</span></span> --&gt; <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「中國共產主義青年團」</span></span>（中國共青團／共青團）<br />\n中國共產主義青年團申請人的加入年齡必須介於14歲至28歲間[4]，共青團同時還主導和監督以14歲以下兒童組成的先鋒組織中國少年先鋒隊[2]。<span style=\"color: teal;\">截至2017年年底，全國共有共青團員8124.6萬名，其中學生團員5795.1萬名；共有基層團組織357.9萬個，其中，基層團委20.4萬個，基層團工委1.6萬個，團總支16.5萬個，團支部319.4萬個，[5]成為世界上規模最大的青年組織之一</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/中國共產主義青年團\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%B1%E7%94%A2%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%A9%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E5%9C%98&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDby6Ol0HYJA13lVA%2BPgi6hPY%3D&h=b7879b19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/中國共產主義青年團</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XOENCD6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXOENCD6.png&h=3f236ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ytgkdcq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYtgkdcq.png&h=29148297&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x2Oyyc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx2Oyyc0.jpg&h=c64a4576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nRGTx1F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnRGTx1F.jpg&h=c494c605&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「童心向党　健康成长」</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣由六歲去到廿八歲</span>，<br />\n咁你話深唔深紅（深藍絲）？</span>"},{"pid":"e555ce49a8bd52ab0df2cd782715cb124705162a","tid":1461647,"uid":123308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:07:27.000Z","msg":"re-post:<br />\n<br />\n正如賣廣告 sell 你嘢，<br />\n一定係刺激你想買嘢嘅 desire，<br />\nemotion-based<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5bq828A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5bq828A.jpg&h=25fa646a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從來唔會講道理講 logic，<br />\n因為一講，要用你錢，你點會捨得買？"},{"pid":"7a09ae1c770d2bba61a62690b18480bc5697ebd3","tid":1461647,"uid":181283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:08:58.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"6836fad46f9ff20fbb790f1f60f14dd26af93bb3","tid":1461647,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e555ce49a8bd52ab0df2cd782715cb124705162a","tid":1461647,"uid":123308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:07:27.000Z","msg":"re-post:<br />\n<br />\n正如賣廣告 sell 你嘢，<br />\n一定係刺激你想買嘢嘅 desire，<br />\nemotion-based<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5bq828A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5bq828A.jpg&h=25fa646a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從來唔會講道理講 logic，<br />\n因為一講，要用你錢，你點會捨得買？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:18:05.000Z","msg":"漏左呢個，thx"},{"pid":"797d703c5cd9355bba74192ff20c819bbd540cf9","tid":1461647,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:18:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"72c1b50dfe40e854d33ab4f33cf136cae1888be3","tid":1461647,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:20:02.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"63cd2634390e647db131ea0087563336760d0c0b","tid":1461647,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:20:17.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"8ead95d13237264bb361e6af2dd505ede458c8b3","tid":1461647,"uid":202633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:22:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"88082b98137b06df40c846a743430d58d1ad0da4","tid":1461647,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:22:24.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"85da6359a7c21ace21d8ac95b0078a417b7132bc","tid":1461647,"uid":300521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:23:48.000Z","msg":"認同，希望上到熱門，加油<br />\n<br />\n[集思廣益] 和你飛副本戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1461170\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1461170</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}